					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">IMO, tile editing programs are too limited, and because everything has to be drawn in little boxes the graphics don't even look very good in the end. You are better off drawing everything in a more capable program, like Paint, Photoshop, GIMP, whatever, and then just converting that into CHR.
<br />
<br />Like others here, I made my own CHR converter with the functions I need, but I think you can paste graphics into YY-CHR, so you can probably use it to convert your graphics without problems.</div>

